e.customer

Interface CustomerDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CustomerDBDAO

    public interface CustomerDAO
    All the methods relevant to customer bean. These methods will be overwritten to allow interface with the relevant Database/file. In this case we are interfacing with Derby DB.
